sources.title: The Jeep (1938)
sources.description: Popeye brings his magical dog, The Jeep, over to see Olive and Swee'pea, just as the tyke has escaped from his crib. The Jeep leads Popeye on a merry chase looking for Swee'pea. Watch on RetroFlix:Â  https://retroflix.org/the-jeep-1938/

metadata.Plot: Olive Oyl has a tough time putting Swee'pea (who keeps on going outside on a wire) for a nap. When Popeye visits Olive, he shows her the Jeep - a dog that can disappear. When Swee'pea disappears again, both Popeye and the Jeep look for him.
